* 01_minimize.inp
* Energy minimization of a protein structure
*

! Load topology and parameters
stream toppar/toppar.str

! Read structure and coordinates
open read card unit 30 name protein.psf
read psf card unit 30

open read card unit 40 name protein.crd
read coor card unit 40

! Nonbonded setup
nbonds atom cdiel eps 1.0 -
    cutnb 14.0 ctofnb 12.0 ctonnb 10.0 -
    switch vatom vswitch

! Fix backbone lightly during steepest descent, then release
cons harm force 5.0 sele type CA .or. type C .or. type N end

mini sd   nstep 250 nprint 50
cons harm clear
mini abnr nstep 750 nprint 50 tolgrd 0.01

energy

! Write minimized coordinates
open write card unit 50 name protein_min.crd
write coor card unit 50
* Minimized coordinates
*

stop
